    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of orangutan living on Sumatra island, they differ from the Bornean orangutan in being smaller and shorter, having lighter and longer hair, a longer face, and flanges that are covered in small white hairs.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
